values ('2b4bcb82c4bf81cdba14d4aa52caa4f1', 'edwardmannix', 'Edward', 'Mannix', 'edwardinbali@gmail.com', '720-527-7722', 'November 23, 2025 12:08 PM', '[{"label":"Who will need to be included in communication about the work we’re doing?","value":"Marjorie MacIntosh (head of marketing) - marjorie@greatbluemarketing.com\nNatalia Delgado (project manager) - natalia@commonbluedms.com"},{"label":"Accounting Contact","value":"Bettina - accounting@compassionkey.com"},{"label":"Who is your IDEAL target customer?","value":"Spiritual seekers who have \"tried everything\" and understand spiritual topics at an intermediate to advanced level. Practitioners in the alternative health space, like energy workers, healers etc. (Roughly 80% professional, 20 % consumer)"},{"label":"Do you have any brand identity or guidelines that you have available for reference? If so, please share the link below:","value":"That is something we are trying to get together right now. Long story short is you will find on the main website a bit of an older version of Edward’s aesthetic. I am working on moving things in a more modern direction. Our brand guide will be more in the direction of the following pages: https://programs.edwardmannix.com/30-day-karma-detox/ and https://programs.edwardmannix.com/master-circle-leader/"},{"label":"What are the PAIN points of the customers you help?","value":"Financial scarcity, health issues, feeling like they aren’t fulfilling their soul’s purpose. They don’t understand why manifesting, energy work, etc haven’t helped them uplevel their life so they can be of service to the world."},{"label":"What are the DESIRED OUTCOMES of the customers you help?","value":"Financial abundance and vibrant health. Living their best life in alignment with their soul’s purpose and helping to create a better world."},{"label":"What is your PROCESS for helping clients get from where they are to where they want to go?","value":"Primarily The Compassion Key, a heart-based Karmic clearing process."},{"label":"Please provide links to some examples of social media clips that you like from a design perspective:","value":"We are open to your ideas. If I can find some before our call I will email."},{"label":"Please provide links to video thumbnails/cover images that you like from a design perspective:","value":"We are open to your ideas. If I can find some before our call I will email."},{"label":"What font preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs? If you are open to our recommendations, please feel free to mention it below:","value":"Use the pages I sent for inspiration here."},{"label":"What color preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs?","value":"I’m thinking the color palette from the shared websites above. Edward generally likes purples alot."},{"label":"Google Drive Link to pictures of yourself","value":"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/2/folders/18ZpxLx6YWvJCncAXGvpKJcDR2VzrxigE"},{"label":"Google Doc Link to links to podcast, speeches or any other video content you want us to create content from","value":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1FIn6F_EY6jJ8qolPUl4vDkQLQeWjZU4Mx8N-gfKkLik/edit?tab=t.0"},{"label":"What would success look like working together?","value":"In the short term: Higher CPA and conversion for leads for our LWA launch from Meta and Youtube ads.\nIn the long term: Lead generation and brand awareness for the Edward Mannix/Compassion Key brands."},{"label":"Anything else we should know?","value":"Not at the moment!"}]'::jsonb, 'notion-legacy', '2025-11-23T12:08:00.000Z')
