values ('294bcb82c4bf81d1acf0c15008396764', 'allischaper', 'Alli', 'Schaper', 'allischaper@gmail.com', '6362841566', 'October 22, 2025 11:08 AM', '[{"label":"Who will need to be included in communication about the work we’re doing?","value":"stacey@supermush.com"},{"label":"Accounting Contact","value":"me :)"},{"label":"Who is your IDEAL target customer?","value":"wellness forward humans, entrepreneurs, psychedelics-advocates, functional mushroom users, people who care about spirituality."},{"label":"Do you have any brand identity or guidelines that you have available for reference? If so, please share the link below:","value":"allischaper.com is a good reference"},{"label":"What are the PAIN points of the customers you help?","value":"people wanting to living a more balanced lifestyle, people wanting to understand grieving, how mushrooms can be a tool to bring the body into balance."},{"label":"What are the DESIRED OUTCOMES of the customers you help?","value":"more joy, more community, more vitality in their lives. Shifting perspectives on the stigmatized topics of society: mushrooms, sexuality, psychedelics, holistic wellness."},{"label":"What is your PROCESS for helping clients get from where they are to where they want to go?","value":"A blend of personal storytelling, science, and spirituality. I love to integrate all three of these into the way that I approach education."},{"label":"Please provide links to some examples of social media clips that you like from a design perspective:","value":"https://www.instagram.com/p/DPZf9SzjhXc/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/DO6xL8jDRek/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/DQAJVMCjrV0/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/DP10PKFDjBT/\nhttps://www.alchemyofartclass.com/waitinglist-rem (like the background style of this with the mic and dimension, not necessarily the sparkly word editing)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/DJFS1bIxRZL/\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/DOtygJbk9lA/\n\nhttps://www.instagram.com/reel/DJzPG8vpcv4/?hl=e (i like the text style and big font on this - not so much the small font, but i think it keeps the video interesting)\nhttps://www.instagram.com/reel/C9Xs8mLthqI/\n\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/DKQK0iaxsYD/ (i like the use of broll here)"},{"label":"Please provide links to video thumbnails/cover images that you like from a design perspective:","value":"https://pin.it/1HktnDiJ3\n\nhttps://pin.it/4VY9MDdET\n\nhttps://pin.it/pRQOg3XlR\n\nhttps://pin.it/4UEA7MUwQ\n\ni would love to have the cover style be a notebook with graphic art around it with the title of each reel and cut out talking heads!"},{"label":"What font preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs? If you are open to our recommendations, please feel free to mention it below:","value":"https://pin.it/5YyTyYKP0\n\nsome ideas here, but open"},{"label":"What color preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs?","value":"colorful! i think purple or blue accent, but i like the idea of alternating colorful titles and different fonts, similar to the reel examples i sent."},{"label":"Google Drive Link to pictures of yourself","value":"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1fsyzQKa1ZxVY9iAQaVQs-4XuirV_bxBJ?usp=drive_link"},{"label":"What would success look like working together?","value":"I''d love to create authentic content that really helps people. I want to reach more people, and translate thoughts and concepts in my head into real life tangible education and information. I want my content to feel real, not salesy, and original. I want it to feel deeply human in a world of the craze of AI social media, and funny when appropriate :)"},{"label":"Anything else we should know?","value":"I''m excited!!\n\nHere''s a story I wrote about my Dad that gives a deeper insight into my perspective on mushrooms, death, psychedelics.\n\nhttps://mushroomseatdeathforbreakfast.tilda.ws/\n\nMy existing social media feed has a lot of content I''ve done before as well, as well as my website allischaper.com\n\nNoting that my account has been shut down about 7 times for referencing mushrooms, psychedelics, etc. (incorrectly, but my account has had many bans on it and I also think I''m shadow banned, i think my account still has the ability to go viral, but it''s more of a struggle). I''d love you to audit my account status and see if anything can be done!"}]'::jsonb, 'notion-legacy', '2025-10-22T11:08:00.000Z')
