values ('35ebcb82c4bf810c84f9d47a34c12dd8', 'henryammar', 'Henry', 'Ammar', 'henry@henryammar.com', '818-535-1616', 'May 11, 2026 8:52 PM', '[{"label":"Who will need to be included in communication about the work we’re doing?","value":"Ava Faught — avakatia0524@gmail.com"},{"label":"Accounting Contact","value":"Me"},{"label":"Who is your IDEAL target customer?","value":"https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/da6id86inumb7gl2fqhju/THE_DEFINITIVE_BRAND_LOCK-IN_DOCUMENT.docx?rlkey=7ajmgjtqlni3s62o3e0afgh1b&e=1&st=jcloj0na&dl=0\n\nSee this doc and the section for it.\n\nVery enticing to elite yet mainstream like Nike effect."},{"label":"What are the PAIN points of the customers you help?","value":"https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/mdm9kjfgqx6d8wtzqk580/Henry-Ammar-Core-Messaging-DNA.docx?rlkey=fh0q43fc0tykwpbtets4exoti&e=1&st=71r7zv8j&dl=0"},{"label":"What are the DESIRED OUTCOMES of the customers you help?","value":"https://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/je7cmrquljrzk06iazt5o/henry_ammar_21_point_strategy_v3.docx?rlkey=xn1vnchkggwk2p4rshifnmh3o&e=1&st=vkck8zhk&dl=0"},{"label":"What is your PROCESS for helping clients get from where they are to where they want to go?","value":"I have a lot of frameworks I need to send over. See some of the docs above for info as well. I will send some over."},{"label":"Please provide links to some examples of social media clips that you like from a design perspective:","value":"https://www.instagram.com/p/DQ5W3AkiT0D/\nhttps://www.tiktok.com/@itsn3t/video/7420445898477538565?lang=en\nhttps://www.instagram.com/reel/DYKZSg3JnZ1/?igsh=MTcybXBiemR6ZjB4Yw==\nhttps://www.instagram.com/reel/DWl-PgApCkp/?igsh=OGpudzV1NWhiM3I0"},{"label":"Please provide links to video thumbnails/cover images that you like from a design perspective:","value":"(Not sure yet. Something between a mainstream account and a higher-end account. Haven''t found one yet. Think Tom Ford meets Alex Hormozi meets Nike — yet personal brand establishing. I''ll send examples when I find the right references. )"},{"label":"What font preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs? If you are open to our recommendations, please feel free to mention it below:","value":"Cormorant Garamond — https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Cormorant+Garamond\n\nProxima Nova — https://fonts.adobe.com/fonts/proxima-nova\n\nOswald — https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Oswald\n\nI am open to it feeling easy to read yet high-end. Commanding, clean, editorial — not decorative or playful."},{"label":"What color preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs?","value":"White subtitles are fine as the primary. I am open to a second accent color that establishes my brand clearly. I currently use yellow but I''d love to find something that feels iconic and elite, yet establishes a clear brand that stands out.\n\nMy recommended palette (from my brand guide ):\n\n• Primary backgrounds: Obsidian Black (#0A0A0A) and Engineered Charcoal (#36454F)\n\n• Primary text: Stark White (#FFFFFF)\n\n• Warm backgrounds (30% of content): Couture Cream (#F4EADE)\n\n• Accent color (used sparingly for emphasis): Authority Gold / Muted Brass (#C69B3C) — this replaces the yellow with something more iconic and elite\n\nNot sure if I like the gold tbh...but something that stands out.\n\nHigh contrast."},{"label":"Google Drive Link to pictures of yourself","value":"https://www.dropbox.com/home/Henry%20Ammar/Companies/Henry%20Ammar%20Brand/Pictures/Pics%20for%20Henry%20to%20Use%20May%202025"},{"label":"What would success look like working together?","value":"Within 6 months, I want to be universally recognized as the definitive authority on the internal game of elite performance. Not just \"another coach on Instagram\" — the undeniable #1 in the human transformation space.\n\nSpecific success metrics:\n\n• Content that commands respect from the highest-level people in the world (billionaires, cultural icons, 9-figure founders watching and sharing)\n\n• High save rates and high DM shares (Sends Per Reach) — people sending my content to their spouse, their business partner, their inner circle\n\n• Inbound leads for my $25K/month Private Advisory coming directly from content\n\n• A feed that looks and feels like a luxury brand — iconic, elite, yet mainstream and accessible\n\n• Viral moments driven by intellectual and emotional dominance — not trends, not dances, not gimmicks\n\n• Building toward: a book launch, arena-scale events, a TV show (Interventions & Breakthroughs), and a cultural movement (Higher Love)\n\nThe goal is 0.01% of the industry. Era-defining. Coming out of nowhere with a grand slam."},{"label":"Anything else we should know?","value":"A few critical things:\n\n1. I am NOT a coach, consultant, motivator, or therapist. I am an advisor who reconstructs the internal operating system of elite leaders. The content must reflect this positioning — never soft, never generic, never \"inspirational quotes.\"\n\n2. My brand voice is called RED ENERGY: bold, dominant, precise, clean, intense, intelligent, emotionally charged, and culturally powerful. Think Kobe Bryant in the fourth quarter. The calmest, most dangerous man in the room.\n\n3. BANNED WORDS (never use in any content): mindset, empower, recode, abundance, hustle, unstoppable, grind, level up, tribe, holding space, unpack, inner child, manifestation, wounded healer, vibrational alignment.\n\n4. I have 30+ proprietary frameworks (67 Faces of Fear, Predictive Emotional Science, ACE Framework, Freedom Formula, Fear Mapping, 5 Levels of Emotional Freedom, etc.) — these are the content fuel. Every piece of teaching content should be built on one of these.\n\n5. I will be sending you a comprehensive Content Manager Grand Slam Guide and Visual Brand Design Guide that contain everything in detail — the full authority stack, framework arsenal, one-liners, leveling statements, content strategy, carousel templates, and visual specs.\n\n6. I will also be creating long-form content alongside the short-form reels — podcast, YouTube, speaking clips. The short-form should feed into and amplify the long-form ecosystem.\n\n7. My credibility stack is my secret weapon — weave it naturally into content: 28+ years, $2B+ in investments, Grammy-winning album, Wharton + USC Magna Cum Laude, 40,000+ person stages, billionaire clients, Forbes, TEDx x2, documentary, $160M fund advisor. Don''t list it like a resume — deploy it like a weapon.\n\nAuthority Stack:\nhttps://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/kfwjgw1wqx0h0a9cw0yh2/HENRY_AUTHORITY_-_CREDIBILITY_STACK.docx?rlkey=o5r2ikbypi2caumrdhh7qli4j&dl=0\n\nSee these as well:\n\nCONTENT STRATEGY MASTER BANK:\nhttps://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/fq0qaavehdjkoj381cuy6/Content_Strategy_Master_Bank.pdf?rlkey=9o34ej6mx0bg4b4es8ysaeeo6&dl=0\n\nhttps://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/eabdjwpyidd87g9tn668i/Content_Strategy_Master_Bank_V_2.pdf?rlkey=njefzekd10za7a875wb18aap2&dl=0\n\nLink of stories and authority (at bottom):\nhttps://www.dropbox.com/scl/fi/w17dxxwd85kwrit971frq/Stories_Master_Document.pdf?rlkey=97ie8kavyt75hrxxx04ax7uq8&dl=0\n\nNote: I will send over speeches and events to use as well. I have a lot of authority establishing content."}]'::jsonb, 'notion-legacy', '2026-05-11T20:52:00.000Z')
