values ('368bcb82c4bf819790afd03a13efae3f', 'lilybaker', 'Lily', 'Baker', 'Drlily@swellwellness.org', '7758133184', 'May 22, 2026 7:37 AM', '[{"label":"Who will need to be included in communication about the work we’re doing?","value":"Jewel -- My VA, not sure how much direct interaction is best yet\naloha@swellwellness.org"},{"label":"Accounting Contact","value":"Dr. John Baker, Drjohn@swellwellness.org"},{"label":"Who is your IDEAL target customer?","value":"The Open Posture Doc speaks most deeply to women who are health-conscious, body-aware, and searching for a deeper understanding of why they still don’t feel fully well in their body despite doing “everything right.” My audience is often made up of moms, former dancers, yogis, Pilates lovers, weight lifters, surfers, athletes, and hypermobile women who care deeply about wellness, movement, beauty, longevity, and nervous system health. Many are high-performing women who are disciplined and proactive about their health, but still feel like something is missing. They are drawn to topics like posture, fascia, feminine vitality, airway health, facial structure, jawline aesthetics, anti-aging, lymph flow, and natural beauty through better body organization rather than force, restriction, or quick fixes. They want to feel elegant, strong, energized, open, connected, and at home in their body again."},{"label":"Do you have any brand identity or guidelines that you have available for reference? If so, please share the link below:","value":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1XC1iWw1UZ3egkoqE_X6yGL755SCijFr1j3Qzr6WYDRY/edit?usp=sharing"},{"label":"What are the PAIN points of the customers you help?","value":"Many of these women have spent years trying different approaches — physical therapy, chiropractic, stretching, strength training, yoga, breathwork, massage, functional medicine, or nervous system work — yet still struggle with chronic tension, instability, tight hips and hamstrings, jaw clenching, mouth breathing, pelvic floor dysfunction, neck pain, poor posture, fatigue, bloating, anxiety, shallow breathing, poor muscle recruitment, or feeling compressed and disconnected in their body. A large portion of my audience is hypermobile or “sensitive-bodied,” meaning they often feel unstable instead of simply tight, and traditional fitness or rehab approaches can leave them feeling worse rather than better. Many are also mothers who are deeply concerned about their children’s posture, airway health, mouth breathing, tongue posture, facial development, nervous system regulation, and overall long-term wellness, and want a more holistic approach to supporting their family. They understand that the way they move, regulate, breathe, and care for themselves impacts the entire household, and they want to lead their family toward health from the inside out. Many also care about the aesthetic side of structure — wanting a more lifted posture, better facial support, improved jawline definition, less tension in the face and neck, healthier aging, and a body that looks as alive and supported as it feels. They are not just looking for exercises — they are looking for a completely different framework for understanding the body, one that blends fascia, biomechanics, nervous system regulation, posture, beauty, movement, and feminine health into a more holistic and integrated approach."},{"label":"What are the DESIRED OUTCOMES of the customers you help?","value":"They buy:\n\\* breathing easier\n\\* less tension\n\\* feeling graceful again\n\\* jaw relaxing\n\\* less exhaustion standing\n\\* stronger glutes naturally\n\\* confidence\n\\* looking more alive/open\n\\* feeling at home in their body\n\\* feeling safe in their body\n\\* finally understanding why nothing worked\n\\* relief\n\\* confidence\n\\* sensuality\n\\* energy\n\\* not feeling broken anymore\n\\* hope"},{"label":"What is your PROCESS for helping clients get from where they are to where they want to go?","value":"Currently I have a virtual class that lays the foundations of better movement and health. That has 500 people in it and would love to get that up to 1,000. I also do virtual 1:1s for people that need more help or to refine their learning from the class for $240/ hour. I will also be launching The Current Collective with you guys — a subscription-based space focused on open posture strength-training workouts, Bowspring, fascial and facial sculpting, and nervous system regulation to help people run more current through their bodies and lives."},{"label":"Please provide links to some examples of social media clips that you like from a design perspective:","value":"1. https://www.instagram.com/p/DW7ipH4Ev2S/?hl=en\n2. https://www.instagram.com/reel/DW3jlLmj4kB/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\n3. https://www.instagram.com/reel/DNwRsvr3H1G/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\n4. https://www.instagram.com/p/CbGZ8KgPNrs/?hl=en&img_index=6 (I like the way she edits photos and the vibe)\n5. https://www.instagram.com/reel/DYCqWAGqVq-/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA== (I feel like this is the only one you guys didn''t make, which is what I mean about natural vibes being really needed on IG right now)\n6. https://www.instagram.com/reel/DYkI9Mgxn_D/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA=="},{"label":"Please provide links to video thumbnails/cover images that you like from a design perspective:","value":"https://www.instagram.com/korimeloy/?hl=en\nI actually like mine currently, I want people to be able to find what they are looking for so I want the cover to be the same or a clip from the video with what it is about, but open to font/ editing of the photo"},{"label":"What font preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs? If you are open to our recommendations, please feel free to mention it below:","value":"open to suggestion but see google doc above"},{"label":"What color preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs?","value":"See googel doc above"},{"label":"Google Drive Link to pictures of yourself","value":"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/13j1zMbD_sx6cvc4ZpkvwMSQuAwvdrV3m?usp=sharing"},{"label":"What would success look like working together?","value":"-- 1,000 people in Repattern\n\\-- 500 monthly subscribers to The Current Collective\n\\-- more sales to my husband''s cream (Catalyst Cream)\n\\-- runway, warm leads for my clothing company (Lily Hoog)\n\\-- 300k followers and growing\n\\-- clean, easy to follow funnels that convert\n\\-- content that I love and have fun making"},{"label":"Anything else we should know?","value":"Very excited to work with you and your team!"}]'::jsonb, 'notion-legacy', '2026-05-22T07:37:00.000Z')
