values ('376bcb82c4bf8148b941c52738aadb6a', 'nickbruss', 'Nick', 'Bruss', 'njbruss@gmail.com', '3109366997', 'June 5, 2026 3:11 PM', '[{"label":"Who will need to be included in communication about the work we’re doing?","value":"for scheduling - hello@apracticeoffreedom.com"},{"label":"Accounting Contact","value":"me"},{"label":"Who is your IDEAL target customer?","value":"curious. anyone interested in being a bit more alive / present. maybe they are curious about or all into psychedelics, meditation, or therapy. or they just find what i''m sharing helpful, that it resonates with them. beyond that, any age, any sex, political, geo, matters not."},{"label":"Do you have any brand identity or guidelines that you have available for reference? If so, please share the link below:","value":"not yet, in the works!"},{"label":"What are the PAIN points of the customers you help?","value":"stuckness. numbness. exhuasted. overwhelm. \"too much\" \"not enough\" grieving, hiding, shame, confusion."},{"label":"What are the DESIRED OUTCOMES of the customers you help?","value":"Freedom. freedom from ____ and freedom to ___ . more presence, more aliveness. larger perspective. self compassion. self love. intimacy. relationship flow. meaningfulness."},{"label":"What is your PROCESS for helping clients get from where they are to where they want to go?","value":"meeting them with the courage and presence for them to be courageous and present with life as it is. I facilitate intimate conversations between clients and their parts- protective parts/patterns and the ones that have been cast out. destination: embodied wholeness"},{"label":"Please provide links to some examples of social media clips that you like from a design perspective:","value":"Blast.. just got lost in IG looking for some. will need to comeback"},{"label":"Please provide links to video thumbnails/cover images that you like from a design perspective:","value":"see above"},{"label":"What font preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs? If you are open to our recommendations, please feel free to mention it below:","value":"working this out, TBD."},{"label":"What color preferences do you have or would you like to see in your designs?","value":"working this out, TBD. bacically blues, greens, some black and gold"},{"label":"Google Drive Link to pictures of yourself","value":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1TgyI9qt9oN0VIHIUxNpxrGHCbs7lbL8hhsDe_qksfmU/edit?usp=sharing"},{"label":"Google Doc Link to links to podcast, speeches or any other video content you want us to create content from","value":"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1M52r-UXsUXXJBHxa2N603LBCyxCyeQHQ_Qhlq3QinOM/edit?usp=sharing"},{"label":"What would success look like working together?","value":"delivering high quality content that educates and empowers, a potent sizzle reel-like home like a business card for potential speaking bookings... and 100k followers (surprise surprise)"},{"label":"Anything else we should know?","value":"I''m looking forward to the strategy session and the list of ideas that you''ll have - seeking engaging fresh ideas beyond my talking head."}]'::jsonb, 'notion-legacy', '2026-06-05T15:11:00.000Z')
